From: 
To 
Cc: ' 
Subject: SDNY Epstein Case 
Date: Fri, 26 Jul 2019 13:51:53 +0000 
Thanks very much for speaking just now. I'm cc'ing the rest of the SDNY Epstein team, including AUSA. 
andl, as well as the lead case agent We really appreciate your 
willingness to 
help with our prosecution and ongoing investigation. 
As discussed, we would ask that any witnesses or victims who contact your office while our case is pending and our 
investigation is ongoing be referred to our team. Once our case is complete, we will refer any matters that were not 
covered by our case and that may be within your jurisdiction to your office. 
Please feel free to contact any of us if any questions or issues arise, and thank you again for your help. 
Maurene 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
I  St. Andrew's Plaza 
New York, NY 10007 
EFTA00021661
